# A bare connection with no metric at all -- exercises the alternate
# entry point (DESIGN-UI.md 6.2/6.4): christoffel/riemann/ricci can work
# from Gamma directly, but scalar/kretschmann need g^ab and must refuse.
manifold M dim 2
bundle TM on M dim 2
chart flat2 on M coords (x, y)
connection Gamma on flat2 {
  [x,y,y] = x
}
